      Overlapping reads all see the <em>same stale value</em>.
    </div>

    <div class="counter-box">
      <div class="counter-label">Counter Value</div>
      <div class="counter-value" id="buggyVal">0</div>
      <div class="expected-row">
        <span>Expected: <strong id="buggyExpected">0</strong></span>
        <span class="lost-label">Lost: <span class="lost-value" id="buggyLost">0</span></span>
