    </div>

    <div class="log-title">Operation Log</div>
    <div class="log" id="fixedLog"></div>

    <div class="timeline-title">Async Timeline (last ops)</div>
    <div class="timeline" id="fixedTimeline"></div>

    <div class="explain">
      <strong>The fix:</strong> A promise chain acts as a mutex.
      Each <code>+1</code> appends to the chain: <code>queue = queue.then(doIncrement)</code>.
      Operations execute <strong>one at a time</strong>, each reading the value
      written by the previous one. Zero increments lost, ever.
    </div>
